Body: Description: I need to update to 5.9.4.2 as per this advisory: https://community.netwrix.com/t/adv-2025-010-insufficient-computational-complexity-in-key-derivation-in-netwrix-endpoint-protector/5299 Howver its not being offerein via live update.
